Control Structure	Purpose	Syntax Example
if	Conditional branching	if [ cond ]; then ... fi
case	Multi-way branching	case var in pattern) ... esac
for	Iterate over list	for var in list; do ... done
C-style for	Counting loop	for ((i=0; i<5; i++)); do ...
while	Loop while condition true	while [ cond ]; do ... done
until	Loop until condition true	until [ cond ]; do ... done
break	Exit loop early	break
continue	Skip iteration	continue
Functions	Encapsulate commands	function name { ... }